						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Parābhava, Phalguṇa, śu. 7.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register a <hi rend="italic">Kavulunāmā</hi> (lease deed) granted to the cultivators <hi rend="italic">(kāmpus)</hi> (of the village) and the others.</p>						

